% $/, $\, $$/, $$\ do not accept doubled (immediate-lookup) forms.
% Each line is a separately scanned snippet; every line raises
% /syntax-error from scan_name's $-prefix dispatch.
{ <($//foo)>#x exec } try clear
{ <($\\foo)>#x exec } try clear
{ <($$//foo)>#x exec } try clear
{ <($$\\foo)>#x exec } try clear
